title: What should we name our token?
body:
We've decided to let the community have a say in naming our token.
Options include:

1. $CATFISH
2. $CATNIP
3. $ZOMCATS
4. $FISHBRAIN
5. $FLESH
6. $ZCAT
7.  $FISHBONE
8. $CATBRAIN

Tokens are an important concept in fractionalizing as they represent your percentage ownership of the vault.

A little more about fractionalizing for those who are new to this concept:

Essentially, fractionalizing means taking an NFT and splitting it into tiny fractions to distribute to many different owners. The distribution is done in the form of customized tokens. 

These owners will, therefore, own a fraction of the NFT. The more tokens you have, the higher your percentage ownership of the NFT.

In our context, we are fractionalizing the ENTIRE ZombieCats Vault. Owners of our tokens will, therefore, own a percentage of the entire vault. 

The more the vault grows, the more your tokens are worth.

The more you stake, the more tokens you earn.

But first, let's decide on the token name.
